1. *Planeta* Marso je četvrta po veličini u Sunčevom sistemu. (The planet Mars is the fourth largest in the Solar System.)

2. *Planeta* Zemlja se okreće oko Sunca za 24 sata. (The planet Earth rotates around the Sun in 24 hours.)

3. *Planetama* se obično nazivaju nebeska tela koja se kreću oko zvezde. (Planets are usually referred to as celestial bodies that move around a star.)

4. *Planeti* su obično okruženi prstenom asteroida. (Planets are usually surrounded by a ring of asteroids.)

5. Naša *planeta* je dom velikom broju životinja. (Our planet is home to a large number of animals.)

6. *Planetu* Uran obasjava Sunčevo svetlo preko 19 godina. (The planet Uranus is bathed in sunlight for over 19 years.)